{"tid":1543952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來成功跳閘真係好爽！多謝連登仔！！","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:00:30.000Z","uid":193592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9b4c3abcb4ce201412eaa396baf278c3102fce","tid":1543952,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"一直都好想跳但成日見到黃人粉人都好淆，每日只敢睇連登羨慕人地既勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係！！<br />\n<br />\n諗返起過去幾個月黨鐵點配合黑社會傷害市民真係太嬲！諗起手足肯為我地擋子彈但我跳都唔敢跳？決心即時增加30%!再不停睇連登大家既跳閘分享，勇氣再提升30%!!!<br />\n<br />\n我著住裙褲唔方便所以其實冇真係做「跳」既動作，首先入閘時拎冇八達通既銀包扮拍，如果係三腳閘，用手拉捉住隻腳拉後再向前chok,紅閘既話，等人多時，扮拍跟人尾出閘！個閘會想關一關但只要你夠快佢唔會真係夾你！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要係扮自然！一氣呵成！唔好怯！！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同我一樣唔膽跳既巴絲可用呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd1d2fb4bf12bc40844e0ddf6f550c9a77b853f","tid":1543952,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"香港歷史上有冇夠 狗屎垃圾 鼠王賤畜芬咁撚厚面皮？<br />\n點解唔成功爭取你老母 生你咁撚厚面皮既畜生既出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDsUKchW4AA-3KM?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDsUKchW4AA-3KM%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=e2ee6be7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a75a112a6f11ea3266ce9df65c855ebc36adc026","tid":1543952,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"加油絲打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721 831<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港警察 強姦謀殺"},{"pid":"0f8aaa7cbac24